          {
            "title": "Lesson #2",
            "id": 130728,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>В TypeScript мы можем сделать аргумент функции необязательным, добавив вопросительный знак <code>?</code> к имени параметра.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"typescript\" name=\"script.ts\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"greet\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"name: \" /><text value=\"string\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\", age?: \" /><text value=\"number\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"): \" /><text value=\"void\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (age !== \" /><text value=\"undefined\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\") {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"`Hello \" /><text value=\"${name}\" class=\"subst\" /><text value=\", you are \" /><text value=\"${age}\" class=\"subst\" /><text value=\" years old.`\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" } \" /><text value=\"else\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"`Hello \" /><text value=\"${name}\" class=\"subst\" /><text value=\" - age not specified.`\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" }\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"32\" endIndex=\"33\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Обязательно выбери <code>?</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #2 - Copy",
            "id": 131054,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Давай вызовем функцию дважды. Сначала укажем только обязательный параметр. Во втором вызове укажем также и необязательный.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"typescript\" name=\"script.ts\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"greet\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"name: \" /><text value=\"string\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\", age?: \" /><text value=\"number\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"): \" /><text value=\"void\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (age !== \" /><text value=\"undefined\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\") {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"`Hello \" /><text value=\"${name}\" class=\"subst\" /><text value=\", you are \" /><text value=\"${age}\" class=\"subst\" /><text value=\" years old.`\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" } \" /><text value=\"else\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"`Hello \" /><text value=\"${name}\" class=\"subst\" /><text value=\" - age not specified.`\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" }\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"greet(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Maria&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"greet(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Maria&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"41\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\");\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"210\" endIndex=\"217\" /><option startIndex=\"226\" endIndex=\"233\" /><option startIndex=\"233\" endIndex=\"234\" /><option startIndex=\"235\" endIndex=\"237\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"&quot;Maria&quot;\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Hello Maria - age not specified.\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Hello Maria, you are 41 years old.\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Обязательно выбери <code>\"Maria\"</code>, затем <code>\"Maria\"</code>, а затем <code>,</code>, <code>41</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #3",
            "id": 130729,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Когда параметр является необязательным, мы можем вызвать функцию, не предоставляя этот аргумент. В этом случае параметр будет <code>undefined</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"typescript\" name=\"script.ts\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"introducePerson\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"name: \" /><text value=\"string\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\", occupation?: \" /><text value=\"string\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"): \" /><text value=\"void\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (occupation !== \" /><text value=\"undefined\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\") {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"`Hello, my name is \" /><text value=\"${name}\" class=\"subst\" /><text value=\" and I am a \" /><text value=\"${occupation}\" class=\"subst\" /><text value=\".`\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" } \" /><text value=\"else\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"   \" /><text value=\"`Hello, my name is \" /><text value=\"${name}\" class=\"subst\" /><text value=\" and my occupation is not specified.`\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" }\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"introducePerson(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Pam&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"introducePerson(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Pam&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;teacher&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"25\" endIndex=\"29\" /><option startIndex=\"31\" endIndex=\"37\" /><option startIndex=\"39\" endIndex=\"49\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"string\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Hello, my name is Pam and my occupation is not specified.\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Hello, my name is Pam and I am a teacher.\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Обязательно выбери <code>name</code>, затем <code>string</code>, и наконец <code>occupation</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #4",
            "id": 130730,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Если мы хотим предоставить значение по умолчанию для аргумента, TypeScript предлагает нам параметры по умолчанию!</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"typescript\" name=\"script.ts\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"calculateTotalPrice\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"price: \" /><text value=\"number\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\", taxRate: \" /><text value=\"number\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\" = 0.05\" /><text value=\"):\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"number\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"return\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" price + (price * taxRate);\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"60\" endIndex=\"61\" /><option startIndex=\"62\" endIndex=\"66\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Обязательно выбери <code>=</code>, а затем <code>0.05</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #4 - Copy",
            "id": 131057,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Параметры со значением по умолчанию могут быть опущены. Вызови функцию дважды. Сначала без указания значения для <code>taxRate</code>, затем укажи его.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"typescript\" name=\"script.ts\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"calculateTotalPrice\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"price: \" /><text value=\"number\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\", taxRate: \" /><text value=\"number\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\" = 0.05\" /><text value=\"):\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"number\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"return\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" price + (price * taxRate);\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(calculateTotalPrice(\" /><text value=\"100\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"));\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(calculateTotalPrice(\" /><text value=\"100\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"0.07\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"));\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"189\" endIndex=\"190\" /><option startIndex=\"191\" endIndex=\"195\" /><option startIndex=\"127\" endIndex=\"151\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"&quot;Price&quot;\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"105\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"107\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Обязательно выбери <code>calculateTotalPrice(100)</code>, затем <code>,</code>, и наконец <code>0.07</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #4 - Copy",
            "id": 131055,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Мы можем даже установить параметр по умолчанию в значение другого параметра. Установите <code>height</code> равным <code>width</code>, если он не передан отдельно.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"typescript\" name=\"script.ts\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"calculateArea\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"width: \" /><text value=\"number\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\", height: \" /><text value=\"number\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\" = width\" /><text value=\"):\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"number\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"return\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" width * height;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(calculateArea(\" /><text value=\"5\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"));\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(calculateArea(\" /><text value=\"5\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"10\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"));\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"23\" endIndex=\"28\" /><option startIndex=\"38\" endIndex=\"44\" /><option startIndex=\"55\" endIndex=\"60\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"25\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"50\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Обязательно выбери <code>width</code>, затем <code>height</code>, и наконец <code>width</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #8",
            "id": 130734,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>TypeScript позволяет нам комбинировать необязательные и параметры по умолчанию.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"typescript\" name=\"script.ts\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"notifyUser\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"message?: \" /><text value=\"string\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\", priority: \" /><text value=\"string\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\" = &quot;normal&quot;\" /><text value=\"):\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"void\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (message === \" /><text value=\"undefined\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\") {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;No message provided&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" } \" /><text value=\"else\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"`Notification: \" /><text value=\"${message}\" class=\"subst\" /><text value=\" (Priority: \" /><text value=\"${priority}\" class=\"subst\" /><text value=\")`\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" }\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"notifyUser();\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"notifyUser(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Your order has been shipped&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"notifyUser(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Your package is delayed&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;high&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"27\" endIndex=\"28\" /><option startIndex=\"55\" endIndex=\"56\" /><option startIndex=\"57\" endIndex=\"65\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"?\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"No message provided\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Notification: Your order has been shipped (Priority: normal)\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Notification: Your package is delayed (Priority: high)\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Обязательно выбери <code>?</code>, затем <code>=</code>, и наконец <code>\"normal\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #5",
            "id": 130731,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Установи параметры по умолчанию для параметров <code>name</code> и <code>age</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"typescript\" name=\"script.ts\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"greet\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"name:\" /><text value=\"string\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\" = &quot;User&quot;, age:\" /><text value=\"string\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\" = &quot;unknown&quot;\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"`Hello \" /><text value=\"${name}\" class=\"subst\" /><text value=\", you are \" /><text value=\"${age}\" class=\"subst\" /><text value=\" years old.`\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"greet();\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"27\" endIndex=\"35\" /><option startIndex=\"48\" endIndex=\"49\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Hello User, you are unknown years old.\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Обязательно выбери <code>= \"User\"</code>, а затем <code>=</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #7",
            "id": 130733,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Может ли функция иметь как необязательные, так и параметры по умолчанию?</p><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\">Да</item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\">Нет</item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Обязательно выбери Да.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #11",
            "id": 131059,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Убедись, что мы предоставляем значение для необязательного параметра.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"typescript\" name=\"script.ts\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"calculateTotal\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"price: \" /><text value=\"number\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\", discount?: \" /><text value=\"number\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"): \" /><text value=\"number\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (discount !== \" /><text value=\"undefined\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\") {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"return\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" price - (price * discount / \" /><text value=\"100\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" }\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"return\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" price;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(calculateTotal(\" /><text value=\"100\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"10\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"));\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"175\" endIndex=\"198\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"calculateTotal(100)\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"90\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Обязательно выбери <code>calculateTotal(100, 10)</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #11",
            "id": 130737,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Что произойдет, если вызвать функцию с необязательным параметром и не предоставить значение для этого параметра?</p><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\">Функция выполняется с <code>undefined</code> для необязательного параметра</item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\">Функция вообще не будет выполняться</item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Функция выполняется с <code>undefined</code> для необязательного параметра.</p></body></html>"
          },
